label: IE TCD MS 3196 / Canon James Goodman
description: Rev. Professor James Goodman's, Canon, collections of Irish folk music; 4 volumes with an index of tunes in each volume. The first 3 volumes are dated 1861, 1863 & 1866 respectively. The 4th volume contains some popular drawingroom music of the period in another hand.
